data.description:
This CHARMING Tudor style home in South Highlands is the cutest house on the street!  It has hardwood floors, elegant decorative lighting and original molding.  You will fall in love with the high ceilings, oversized windows and quaint butlers pantry typical for 1940's style architectural. Mature oak trees adorn the newly fenced backyard providing lots of natural shade for additional parking behind a security gate. This lovely home has been meticulously maintained! All new 2023 stainless steel appliances will stay with the home.  The roof was replaced in 2020 and HVAC system regularly serviced every 6 months.  Experience the Mardi Gras Highland Parade with your wonderful neighbors and friends from your own front porch!  
This gem will not last long! Schedule an appointment today!
